"and replace every <literal>hda</literal>, <literal>hdb</literal>, "
"<literal>hdc</literal>, <literal>hdd</literal> with <literal>sda</literal>, "
"<literal>sdb</literal>, <literal>sdc</literal>, <literal>sdd</literal>, as "
"appropriate.  Don't modify the line similar to:"
msgstr ""
"và thay thế mỗi chuỗi <literal>hda</literal>, <literal>hdb</literal>, "
"<literal>hdc</literal>, <literal>hdd</literal> bằng<literal>sda</literal>, "
"<literal>sdb</literal>, <literal>sdc</literal>, <literal>sdd</literal> như "
"thích hợp.  Không nên sửa đổi dòng tương tự với:"

